      <p>
       <strong>
        Did you Know
       </strong>
      </p>
      <p>
       All  employee expenses, regardless of whether  they were out-of-pocket or GEMS card expenses, must be reconciled using  the GEMS system, with the exception of small  amounts reimbursed via Petty Cash and expenses related to a Travel Advance.  Expenses to  clear a Travel Advance must continue to be processed via
       <a href="https://shibboleth2.uchicago.edu/idp/Authn/MCB">
        ePayment
       </a>
       .
      </p>
